Happy Love Day❤️❤️❤️:
Currently, I’m very happy & feeling all the mushies. 🥰🌺

Sharing a few things that got me through heartache as I KNOW it will help many of you too. ⬇️

🌸Let your spirit & discernment guide your love life… not your 🐱or your 🍆.

🌺You are your first love & the love of your life. 

🌸DATE YOURSELF FIRST. So you know what you want and how you want to be treated.

🌺You deserve the love you desire, but don’t forget to prepare yourself to receive it. 

🌸Stop letting them waste your time. 

🌺Stop being stuck on that mf’ that still wanna dabble into every other person but you.

🌸Stop waiting around for them. On & off just means boredom & toxicity. 

🌺If they ain’t coming around with permanent changes, it will NEVER be different.

🌸I know you a thug at heart, but thugs need love too. Don’t be afraid to be mushy to the one that’s showing their true desires for you.

🌺COMPATIBILITY IS JUST AS IMPORTANT AS CHEMISTRY AND ATTRACTION. 

🌸Keep it playa until your spirit says they’re the one.

**& to my my stalker ex that refuses to let it go after only dating for a couple months YEARS AGO. The last slide is for YOU. 🙃
